ncluding three dual riffle pans, two mini classifiers, a snifter bottle, a black sand magnet tool, sand scoop, and gold storage vial.</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">3 DUAL RIFFLE GOLD PANS FOR BETTER RECOVERY - Includes 8\", 10\", and 12\" pans with dual riffle designs that help trap fine gold flakes while washing away lighter sand and gravel.</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">CLASSIFY MATERIAL FOR FASTER PANNING - Two mini 6\" classifiers (30 holes/inch &amp; 10 holes/inch) help separate rocks and concentrate paydirt for more efficient gold recovery.</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">BLACK SAND MAGNET WITH QUICK RELEASE - Portable 8lb magnetic pickup tool quickly removes magnetic black sand from concentrates; quick-release handle makes cleanup easy.</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">FINE GOLD RECOVERY TOOLS - Includes a 3oz snifter bottle for capturing fine flakes and a 2 dram glass vial to safely store your gold finds.</td>\n                            </tr>\n                        </tbody>\n                    </table>\n                </div><!-- /product-specs -->\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n                <h1>ASR Outdoor 9pc Gold Prospecting Kit with Mini Classifiers Gold Pans and Collection Tools</h1>\n                <h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">59.99</span></h2>\n                <p>Strike gold with the ASR Outdoor 9pc Gold Panning Kit, a complete prospecting set designed for beginners and experienced gold hunters alike. Whether you're exploring rivers, creeks, or paydirt at home, this kit includes the essential tools needed to efficiently separate gold from sand, gravel, and black sand concentrates.<br><br>\nThe kit features three dual riffle gold pans (8\", 10\", and 12\") that allow you to process material at different stages of your prospecting workflow. Use the mini classifier sieves to sort gravel and concentrate your material for faster, more efficient panning.<br><br>A large 12.5\" sand scoop trowel makes collecting paydirt quick and easy, while the 3oz snifter bottle helps you safely collect fine gold flakes from the pan. Once separated, store your finds in the included 2 dram glass vial to keep your gold safe and secure.<br><br>To make cleanup even easier, the kit also includes a powerful, portable magnetic black-sand pickup tool with a quick-release handle. This tool helps remove heavy black sand from your concentrates, making it easier to spot and collect valuable gold.<br><br>Compact, lightweight, and easy to transport, the ASR Outdoor Gold Panning Kit is perfect for weekend prospecting trips, family adventures, geology enthusiasts, and hobbyists looking to experience the excitement of gold discovery.</p>\n                <div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n                    <div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n                    <div class=\"grid-100\">\n                        <p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n                        <p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n                        <a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&amp;sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n 